reviews.text: No number to call for information that actually works..... 15 mins hanging on the phone for customer services and complaints, ha ha... what a joke?!?!?   Total waste of time,  it was not even for me, my mother was told cannot buy tickets in advance?? Only when on the train.... another waste of time in so many ways!!   All train companies seem to be all about helping  themselves than others... would not want to be reliant on a train to get a round,  hence why there so many people driving and not using public transport...
